cx=\"50\" cy=\"33\" rx=\"4.5\" ry=\"6\" fill=\"#222\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"14\" cy=\"33\" rx=\"4.5\" ry=\"6\" fill=\"#222\"></ellipse><path d=\"M20 46c0-8 5-12 12-12s12 4 12 12-5 10-12 10-12-2-12-10z\" fill=\"#222\"></path></svg><span style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.2px\">Paws&amp;Tales</span></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-8\"><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--color-on-primary)]\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--color-on-primary)]\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/categories\">Categories</a><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--color-on-primary)]\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/authors\">Authors</a><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--color-on-primary)]\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--color-on-primary)]\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></nav><div class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center transition-colors\" style=\"background:var(--color-primary);color:var(--color-on-primary);border-radius:32px;height:48px;padding:0 24px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;border:2px solid var(--color-primary)\" href=\"/blog\">Read the journal</a></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"lg:hidden inline-flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:9999px;border:2px solid var(--color-ink);background:transparent;color:var(--color-ink)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></header><main style=\"flex:1\"><section style=\"background:var(--color-surface-soft)\"><div class=\"mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 py-12 lg:py-20\" style=\"max-width:1444px\"><div style=\"max-width:760px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-muted)\">The team</span><h1 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:16px\">Real people, real dogs, real care.</h1><p style=\"font-size:18px;color:var(--color-body);line-height:1.6\">Vets, trainers, behaviour specialists and lifelong dog people — each of our authors writes from years of looking after dogs and their humans.</p></div></div></section><section style=\"background:var(--color-canvas)\"><div class=\"mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 py-12 lg:py-20\" style=\"max-width:1444px\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8\"><a style=\"background:var(--color-canvas);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);box-shadow:0 0 9px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease\" class=\"hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_6px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)]\" href=\"/authors/aaron-whyte\"><div class=\"relative shrink-0\" style=\"width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-surface)\"><img alt=\"Aaron Whyte\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1633332755192-727a05c4013d?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=400&amp;q=80\"/></div><div style=\"flex:1\"><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px\">Aaron Whyte</h3><p style=\"color:var(--color-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:3;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden\">Detection and scentwork trainer turned enrichment specialist. Writes on play, enrichment and rainy-day activities.</p><span style=\"margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-muted)\">632<!-- --> article<!-- -->s</span></div></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-canvas);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);box-shadow:0 0 9px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease\" class=\"hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_6px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)]\" href=\"/authors/marcus-aldridge\"><div class=\"relative shrink-0\" style=\"width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-surface)\"><img alt=\"Marcus Aldridge\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=400&amp;q=80\"/></div><div style=\"flex:1\"><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px\">Marcus Aldridge</h3><p style=\"color:var(--color-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:3;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden\">Certified clinical animal behaviourist (CCAB, ASAB) specialising in reactive and rescue dogs. Leads our behaviour content team.</p><span style=\"margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-muted)\">628<!-- --> article<!-- -->s</span></div></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-canvas);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);box-shadow:0 0 9px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease\" class=\"hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_6px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)]\" href=\"/authors/priya-sutaria\"><div class=\"relative shrink-0\" style=\"width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-surface)\"><img alt=\"Priya Sutaria\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=400&amp;q=80\"/></div><div style=\"flex:1\"><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px\">Priya Sutaria</h3><p style=\"color:var(--color-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:3;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden\">Force-free dog trainer (IMDT) and Karen Pryor Academy graduate. Writes our basics-to-advanced training how-tos.</p><span style=\"margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-muted)\">686<!-- --> article<!-- -->s</span></div></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-canvas);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);box-shadow:0 0 9px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease\" class=\"hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_6px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)]\" href=\"/authors/jonas-cole\"><div class=\"relative shrink-0\" style=\"width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-surface)\"><img alt=\"Jonas Cole\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=400&amp;q=80\"/></div><div style=\"flex:1\"><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px\">Jonas Cole</h3><p style=\"color:var(--color-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:3;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden\">Puppy and adolescent dog specialist (KPA-CTP). Coaches first-time owners through the puppy stage and beyond.</p><span style=\"margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-muted)\">600<!-- --> article<!-- -->s</span></div></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-canvas);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);box-shadow:0 0 9px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease\" class=\"hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_6px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)]\" href=\"/authors/anouk-beaumont\"><div class=\"relative shrink-0\" style=\"width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-surface)\"><img alt=\"Anouk Beaumont\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=400&amp;q=80\"/></div><div style=\"flex:1\"><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px\">Anouk Beaumont</h3><p style=\"color:var(--color-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:3;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden\">Canine welfare researcher (PhD, applied animal behaviour). Writes our long-form guides on body language and welfare.</p><span style=\"margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-muted)\">579<!-- --> article<!-- -->s</span></div></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-canvas);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);box-shadow:0 0 9px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease\" class=\"hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_6px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)]\" href=\"/authors/tom-renshaw\"><div class=\"relative shrink-0\" style=\"width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-surface)\"><img alt=\"Tom Renshaw\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=400&amp;q=80\"/></div><div style=\"flex:1\"><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px\">Tom Renshaw</h3><p style=\"color:var(--color-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:3;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden\">Veterinary nurse (RVN) and clinical writer. Translates vet practice into plain-language advice for owners at home.</p><span style=\"margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-muted)\">588<!-- --> article<!-- -->s</span></div></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-canvas);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);box-shadow:0 0 9px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease\" class=\"hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_6px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)]\" href=\"/authors/beth-carrasco\"><div class=\"relative shrink-0\" style=\"width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-surface)\"><img alt=\"Beth Carrasco\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554151228-14d9def656e4?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=400&amp;q=80\"/></div><div style=\"flex:1\"><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px\">Beth Carrasco</h3><p style=\"color:var(--color-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:3;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden\">Adoption coordinator and lifestyle editor. Writes on choosing a dog, life-with-your-dog and home-readiness.</p><span style=\"margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-muted)\">569<!-- --> article<!-- -->s</span></div></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-canvas);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);box-shadow:0 0 9px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease\" class=\"hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_6px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)]\" href=\"/authors/robin-maitland\"><div class=\"relative shrink-0\" style=\"width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-surface)\"><img alt=\"Robin Maitland\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607746882042-944635dfe10e?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=400&amp;q=80\"/></div><div style=\"flex:1\"><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px\">Robin Maitland</h3><p style=\"color:var(--color-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:3;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden\">Recall and outdoor-skills coach. Writes on lead handling, recall, and life-on-walks problem solving.</p><span style=\"margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-muted)\">574<!-- --> article<!-- -->s</span></div></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-canvas);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);box-shadow:0 0 9px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease\" class=\"hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_6px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10)]\" href=\"/authors/hannah-wickes\"><div class=\"relative shrink-0\" style=\"width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-surface)\"><img alt=\"Dr. Hannah Wickes\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=400&amp;q=80\"/></div><div style=\"flex:1\"><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px\">Dr. Hannah Wickes</h3><p style=\"color:var(--color-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:3;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden\">Veterinary surgeon (BVSc, MRCVS) with twelve years of small-animal clinical experience. Writes our health, nutrition and at-home vet-care guides.</p><span style=\"margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-muted)\">632<!-- --> article<!-- -->s</span></div></a></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer style=\"background:var(--color-surface-footer);color:#f7edce\"><div style=\"background:var(--color-primary);color:var(--color-on-primary)\"><div class=\"mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 py-10 lg:py-